      <title><![CDATA[css常用选择器（一）]]></title>
      <url>/blog/2017/07/10/676848e4.html</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;CSS是 <code>Cascading Style Sheet</code> (层叠样式表)的缩写。 <code>cascade</code> （重叠）表示CSS的冲突规则，即如果有样式冲突，则将新的样式覆盖在旧的样式之上。<br><a id="more"></a></p><h3 id="CSS规则结构"><a href="#CSS规则结构" class="headerlink" title="CSS规则结构"></a>CSS规则结构</h3><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="selector-tag">h1</span> &#123;<span class="attribute">color</span>:deepskyblue;&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>每个CSS规则都有两个基本部分，<code>h1</code> 表示选择器(selector) ，<code>{color:deepskyblue;}</code> 表示声明块(declaration block)。那么CSS中都有哪些常用的选择器呢？CSS中选择器基本分为五类：基本选择器、关系选择器、属性选择器、伪类选择器和伪元素选择器。<br><img src="http://osjk6wlzk.bkt.clouddn.com/css/selector/CSS-selector-1.png" alt="image"></p><h3 id="基本选择器"><a href="#基本选择器" class="headerlink" title="基本选择器"></a>基本选择器</h3><p>基本选择器主要由通配符选择器、元素（标签）选择器、ID选择器和类名选择器组成。</p><h4 id="通配符选择器"><a href="#通配符选择器" class="headerlink" title="通配符选择器( * )"></a>通配符选择器( * )</h4><p>通配符选择器，你可以使用 <code>*</code> 命中所有的元素。出于对性能的考虑，通常不建议使用它。</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span><span class="css"></span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">/*将所有元素的颜色设置为红色*/</span></div><div class="line">* &#123;</div><div class="line">  <span class="attribute">color</span>:red;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">h1</span>&gt;</span> Head Title Lv1. <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">h1</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">h2</span>&gt;</span> Head Title Lv2. <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">h2</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line">	...</div><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">h6</span>&gt;</span> Head Title Lv6. <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">h6</span>&gt;</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="元素（标签）选择器"><a href="#元素（标签）选择器" class="headerlink" title="元素（标签）选择器"></a>元素（标签）选择器</h4><p>元素选择器，是直接使用Html的标签元素作为选择器。例如: <code>h1 {color:deepskyblue;}</code> ,h1这个选择器会命中Html文档中所有的h1元素，将所有h1元素的字体颜色设置为red。</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span><span class="css"></span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">/*将所有 h1 元素的颜色设置为红色*/</span></div><div class="line"><span class="selector-tag">h1</span> &#123;	</div><div class="line">  <span class="attribute">color</span>:red;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line">...</div><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">h1</span>&gt;</span> Head Title Lv1. <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">h1</span>&gt;</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="ID选择器"><a href="#ID选择器" class="headerlink" title="ID选择器"></a>ID选择器</h4><blockquote><p>注意：Html元素的id属性是唯一的，这意味这你不能给不同的元素使用相同的id属性值。</p></blockquote><p>使用ID选择器前,必须给Html的标签加上一个名为 <code>id</code> 的属性，该属性的值必须是<code>合法的标识符</code>,然后在样式表中通过 <code># + id</code>属性值 来选中元素；</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span><span class="css"></span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">/*将id为identitied的元素颜色设置为红色*/</span></div><div class="line"><span class="selector-id">#identitied</span> &#123;</div><div class="line">  <span class="attribute">color</span>:red;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line">...</div><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">id</span>=<span class="string">"identified"</span>&gt;</span>这是一个id为identified的div元素<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="类名选择器"><a href="#类名选择器" class="headerlink" title="类名选择器"></a>类名选择器</h4><p>类名选择器允许你命中一批元素,但前提是你必须给他们加上一个名为 <code>class</code>的属性，并设置相同的属性值，同样该属性的值必须是<code>合法的标识符</code>,然后在样式表中通过 <code>. + class属性值</code>来选中元素。</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span><span class="css"></span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">/*将class为clz的元素颜色设置为红色*/</span></div><div class="line"><span class="selector-class">.clz</span> &#123;</div><div class="line">  <span class="attribute">color</span>:red;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line">...</div><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">h1</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"clz"</span>&gt;</span> Head Title Lv1. <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">h1</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"clz"</span>&gt;</span>这是一个class为clz的div元素<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">section</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"clz"</span>&gt;</span>这是一个class为clz的section元素<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">section</span>&gt;</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="关系选择器"><a href="#关系选择器" class="headerlink" title="关系选择器"></a>关系选择器</h3><p>关系选择器包括：后代选择器、子元素选择器、相邻兄弟选择器和普通兄弟选择器。</p><h4 id="后代选择器"><a href="#后代选择器" class="headerlink" title="后代选择器"></a>后代选择器</h4><blockquote><p><code>S</code> 表示 选择器( Selector )</p></blockquote><p>后代选择器的语法通常为：<code>S1 S2</code> ,在两个选择器之间存在一个空格,该选择器命中所有被S1元素包含的S2元素;</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span><span class="css"></span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">/*将s1下所有的s2设置为红色*/</span></div><div class="line"><span class="selector-class">.s1</span> <span class="selector-class">.s2</span> &#123;</div><div class="line">  <span class="attribute">color</span>:red;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line">...</div><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"s1"</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line">	<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"s2"</span>&gt;</span>红色文本</div><div class="line">		<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"s2"</span>&gt;</span>红色文本<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line">	<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"s2"</span>&gt;</span>黑色文本<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="子元素选择器"><a href="#子元素选择器" class="headerlink" title="子元素选择器"></a>子元素选择器</h4><p>子元素选择器的语法通常为：<code>S1 &gt; S2</code> ,该选择器命中被S1元素包含的第一层S2元素;<br></p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span><span class="css"></span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">/*将s1下第一层的s2设置为红色*/</span></div><div class="line"><span class="selector-class">.s1</span> &gt; <span class="selector-class">.s2</span> &#123;</div><div class="line">  <span class="attribute">color</span>:red;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line">...</div><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"s1"</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line">	<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"s2"</span>&gt;</span>红色文本</div><div class="line">		<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"s2"</span>&gt;</span>黑色文本<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line">	<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line">	<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"s2"</span>&gt;</span>红色文本</div><div class="line">		<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"s2"</span>&gt;</span>黑色文本<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line">	<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"s2"</span>&gt;</span>黑色文本<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p></p><h4 id="相邻兄弟选择器"><a href="#相邻兄弟选择器" class="headerlink" title="相邻兄弟选择器"></a>相邻兄弟选择器</h4><p>相邻兄弟选择器的语法通常为：<code>S1 + S2</code> ,该选择器命中紧挨着S1元素，并且在S1之后的S2元素;<br></p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span><span class="css"></span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">/*将紧挨着s1，并且在s1之后的s2设置为红色*/</span></div><div class="line"><span class="selector-class">.s1</span> + <span class="selector-class">.s2</span> &#123;</div><div class="line">  <span class="attribute">color</span>:red;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line">...</div><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"s2"</span>&gt;</span>黑色文本<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"s1"</span>&gt;</span>黑色文本<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"s2"</span>&gt;</span>红色文本<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p></p><p>如果在某些情况下，你只需要设置除了第一个元素之外的样式，可以像下面这样写，这样巧妙的剔除了第一个元素；<br>像类似这种 <code>* + *</code> 的选择器，又称为”猫头鹰选择器”。<br></p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span><span class="css"></span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">/*将紧挨着s1，并且在s1之后的s2设置为红色*/</span></div><div class="line"><span class="selector-class">.s2</span> + <span class="selector-class">.s2</span> &#123;</div><div class="line">  <span class="attribute">color</span>:red;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line">...</div><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"s2"</span>&gt;</span>黑色文本<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"s2"</span>&gt;</span>红色文本<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"s2"</span>&gt;</span>红色文本<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p></p><h4 id="普通兄弟选择器"><a href="#普通兄弟选择器" class="headerlink" title="普通兄弟选择器"></a>普通兄弟选择器</h4><p>普通兄弟选择器的语法通常为：<code>S1 ~ S2</code> ,该选择器命中所有在S1之后的S2元素;<br></p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span><span class="css"></span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">/*将在s1之后的s2设置为红色*/</span></div><div class="line"><span class="selector-class">.s1</span> ~ <span class="selector-class">.s2</span> &#123;</div><div class="line">  <span class="attribute">color</span>:red;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line">...</div><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"s1"</span>&gt;</span>黑色文本<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"s2"</span>&gt;</span>红色文本<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"s2"</span>&gt;</span>红色文本<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p></p><h3 id="属性选择器"><a href="#属性选择器" class="headerlink" title="属性选择器"></a>属性选择器</h3><p>属性选择器是通过元素中已经存在的属性名或属性值匹配元素。</p><h4 id="attr"><a href="#attr" class="headerlink" title="[attr]"></a>[attr]</h4><p><code>[attr]</code> 将会选中页面中带有attr属性的元素，无论该元素是否有值。<br></p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span><span class="css"></span></div><div class="line">    <span class="selector-tag">li</span><span class="selector-attr">[class]</span> &#123;</div><div class="line">        <span class="attribute">background</span>:deepskyblue;</div><div class="line">    &#125;</div><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line"> ...</div><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">""</span> &gt;</span>0<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p></p><h4 id="attr-”value”"><a href="#attr-”value”" class="headerlink" title="[attr=”value”]"></a>[attr=”value”]</h4><p><code>[attr=&quot;value&quot;]</code> 将会选中页面中带有attr属性，且属性值为<code>value</code>的元素。</p><pre><code class="html"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span><span class="css">
    <span class="selector-tag">li</span><span class="selector-attr">[class="num-zero"]</span> {
        <span class="attribute">background</span>:deepskyblue;
    }
</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span>
 ...
<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"num-zero"</span> &gt;</span>0<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span>
</code></pre><h4 id="attr-”value”-1"><a href="#attr-”value”-1" class="headerlink" title="[attr~=”value”]"></a>[attr~=”value”]</h4><p><code>[attr~=&quot;value&quot;]</code> 将会选中页面中带有attr属性，且属性值是一个以空格分隔的属性值列表，而其中至少有一个属性值为value。</p><pre><code class="html"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span><span class="css">
    <span class="selector-tag">li</span><span class="selector-attr">[class~="num-zero"]</span> {
        <span class="attribute">background</span>:deepskyblue;
    }
</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span>
 ...
<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"num-zero zero"</span> &gt;</span>0<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span>
</code></pre><h4 id="attr-”value”-2"><a href="#attr-”value”-2" class="headerlink" title="[attr^=”value”]"></a>[attr^=”value”]</h4><p><code>[attr^=&quot;value&quot;]</code> 将会选中页面中带有attr属性，且属性值是以value开头的元素；</p><pre><code class="html"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span><span class="css">
    <span class="selector-tag">li</span><span class="selector-attr">[class^="num"]</span> {
        <span class="attribute">background</span>:deepskyblue;
    }
</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span>
 ...
<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"num-zero"</span> &gt;</span>0<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span>
</code></pre><h4 id="attr-”value”-3"><a href="#attr-”value”-3" class="headerlink" title="[attr|=”value”]"></a>[attr|=”value”]</h4><p><code>[attr|=&quot;value&quot;]</code> 将会选中带有attr属性,且属性值是以value或者value- 开头的元素；</p><pre><code class="html"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span><span class="css">
    <span class="selector-tag">li</span><span class="selector-attr">[class|="num"]</span> {
        <span class="attribute">background</span>:deepskyblue;
    }
</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span>
 ...
<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"num-zero"</span> &gt;</span>0<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span>
</code></pre><h4 id="attr-”value”-4"><a href="#attr-”value”-4" class="headerlink" title="[attr$=”value”]"></a>[attr$=”value”]</h4><p><code>[attr$=&quot;value&quot;]</code> 将会选中带有attr属性,且属性值已value结尾的元素</p><pre><code class="html"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span><span class="css">
    <span class="selector-tag">li</span><span class="selector-attr">[class$="zero"]</span> {
        <span class="attribute">background</span>:deepskyblue;
    }
</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span>
 ...
<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"num-zero"</span> &gt;</span>0<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span>
</code></pre><h4 id="attr-”value”-5"><a href="#attr-”value”-5" class="headerlink" title="[attr*=”value”]"></a>[attr*=”value”]</h4><p><code>[attr*=&quot;value&quot;]</code> 将会选中带有attr属性，且属性值中包含value的元素</p><pre><code class="html"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span><span class="css">
    <span class="selector-tag">li</span><span class="selector-attr">[class*="zero"]</span> {
        <span class="attribute">background</span>:deepskyblue;
    }
</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span>
 ...
<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"num-zero"</span> &gt;</span>0<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span>
</code></pre><div style="text-align:center;margin-top:100px"><strong style="font-size:20px">— EOF —</strong></div>]]></content>
      
